high_descs: Go forward, before reaching the dresser turn right, go forward, turn left after passing the couch, go forward to the wall, turn right, go forward to the desk.
Turn the lamp on the desk on.
Take the clock from the desk.

high_descs: Hang a right at the wooden dresser, take a left to the wall after the couch and walk to the wooden desk on the right.
Turn on the small lamp in the left corner of the desk.
Pick up the clock to the right of the small lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a clock by the light of a small lamp.

high_descs: pick up clock from the desk
